text: I like that their fried chicken is cut into easily eaten chunks. No complains about the tasty fried chicken and the pork floss egg crepe is also good. Menu is a little limited but they are more like a food kiosk so that is understandable. The only gripe I have is that sometimes when the stall is busy, they have only One staff. The poor staff has to collect money, take order, fry the chicken, cut the chicken etc. Your staff not actually super humans okay?
Need to eat it right away so you can enjoy the fresh crisp from the chicken skin. Tasted hot and well cooked.
Ordered takeaway, was missing one chicken. Very upset i was extremely hungry.  took the order on 5/8, She was wearing ponytail & chinese. Hopefully can get a refund.

Staff are usually nice and polite. However, the chicken cutlet I got today is FULL OF FATS. Layers and layers of FATS. Please QC or feedback to supplier. Will not buy again if its full of fats in next purchase.
